These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, potato
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is not the person eating potato##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | potato   | cucumber  |
| Sport   | parkour | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, corn
2 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the mouse is not the person eating corn##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | broccoli | corn      |
| Pet    | mouse  | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
