.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, architect
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard
1. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
2. the mechanic is not the owner of the lizard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | mechanic | architect |
| Pet   | hedgehog       | lizard       |

